It'll only take a second.

07:36.046 --> 07:37.712
Monk, you cannot read that.

07:37.887 --> 07:39.090
Wait, wait, wait- oh, my God, wait.

07:39.175 --> 07:40.363
Monk. That's it. That's it.

07:40.457 --> 07:41.783
You've crossed the line.
Out of here.

07:53.266 --> 07:54.690
Okay.

08:00.968 --> 08:02.331
You okay?

08:03.905 --> 08:06.441
I... saw something in my file.

08:07.197 --> 08:08.951
Oh, Mr. Monk. I told you not to look.

08:12.876 --> 08:14.231
What was it?

08:15.092 --> 08:17.029
Two words at the bottom of the page.

08:18.347 --> 08:19.243
Two words.

08:19.596 --> 08:20.913
What did it say?

08:21.856 --> 08:23.743
"No hope. "

08:28.585 --> 08:33.470
She worked for me, cleaning
my office, for... 10, 12 years.

08:33.575 --> 08:35.361
I- I didn't really know her.

08:35.828 --> 08:39.971
- I think she had a daughter.
- Yeah, one daughter in Santa Fe.

08:40.207 --> 08:41.663
No other family, though.

08:42.417 --> 08:43.760
- It's terrible.
- Yeah.

08:43.888 --> 08:46.062
Doc, you know, the door wasn't jimmied.

08:46.185 --> 08:47.172
Somebody had a key.

08:48.145 --> 08:49.600
Who elsehas a key to your office?

08:50.375 --> 08:54.081
- Just me. And Teresa.
- What about your patients?

08:55.337 --> 08:57.041
My patients?
No, of course not.

08:57.497 --> 08:59.691
Well, there was an extra set
of keys in the desk out front.

09:00.175 --> 09:01.160
Which wasn't locked.

09:01.346 --> 09:03.240
Somebody could've lifted
the mand made a copy.

09:03.638 --> 09:05.620
