one of my patients...

09:06.258 --> 09:07.972
To be honest with you,Doc,
that's how it looks.

09:08.205 --> 09:10.593
We figure somebody broke
in,looking for a file.

09:10.728 --> 09:11.900
Probably his own file.

09:14.498 --> 09:16.882
Look, I realize that
you're reluctant here,

09:17.038 --> 09:18.763
but I happen to be a homicide detective,

09:18.898 --> 09:21.030
and this happens to be
a homicide investigation.

09:21.085 --> 09:22.791
I- I understand.

09:22.917 --> 09:24.921
I truly hope you do, because
if you do know something-

09:25.698 --> 09:28.322
If you believe one of your
patients could be involved in this,

09:28.417 --> 09:30.510
